            <title>[HIVE-884] Metastore Server should exit if error happens</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HIVE-884</link>
                <project id="12310843" key="HIVE">Hive</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently, HiveMetaStore (the thrift server) is not exiting when the main thread saw an Exception.&lt;br/&gt;
